trans-unit.source: Defines access levels used by <see cref="T:System.Diagnostics.EventLog" /> permission classes.
trans-unit.target: Define os níveis de acesso usados pelas classes de permissão <see cref="T:System.Diagnostics.EventLog" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Diagnostics.EventLog" /> can create an event source, read existing logs, delete event sources or logs, respond to entries, clear an event log, listen to events, and access a collection of all event logs.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.Diagnostics.EventLog" /> pode criar uma fonte de evento, ler logs existentes, excluir fontes de eventos ou logs, responder a entradas, limpar um log de eventos, escutar eventos e acessar uma coleção de todos os logs de eventos.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Diagnostics.EventLog" /> can read existing logs, delete event sources or logs, respond to entries, clear an event log, listen to events, and access a collection of all event logs.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.Diagnostics.EventLog" /> pode ler logs existentes, excluir fontes de eventos ou logs, responder a entradas, limpar um log de eventos, escutar eventos e acessar uma coleção de todos os logs de eventos.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="Note" /> This member is now obsolete, use <see cref="F:System.Diagnostics.EventLogPermissionAccess.Administer" /> instead.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="Note" /> Esse membro agora está obsoleto, use <see cref="F:System.Diagnostics.EventLogPermissionAccess.Administer" /> no lugar dele.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Diagnostics.EventLog" /> can read existing logs.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.Diagnostics.EventLog" /> pode ler logs existentes.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="Note" /> This member is now obsolete, use <see cref="F:System.Diagnostics.EventLogPermissionAccess.Administer" /> instead.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="Note" /> Esse membro agora está obsoleto, use <see cref="F:System.Diagnostics.EventLogPermissionAccess.Administer" /> no lugar dele.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Diagnostics.EventLog" /> can read or write to existing logs, and create event sources and logs.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.Diagnostics.EventLog" /> pode ler ou gravar em logs existentes e criar fontes de eventos e logs.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="Note" /> This member is now obsolete, use <see cref="F:System.Diagnostics.EventLogPermissionAccess.Write" /> instead.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="Note" /> Esse membro agora está obsoleto, use <see cref="F:System.Diagnostics.EventLogPermissionAccess.Write" /> no lugar dele.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Diagnostics.EventLog" /> can write to existing logs, and create event sources and logs.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.Diagnostics.EventLog" /> pode gravar em logs existentes e criar fontes de eventos e logs.
